title: Cate Blanchett to visit India for Women in the World summit
text:
Hollywood diva Cate Blanchett will make her maiden trip to India next month for the prestigious World in the World summit, reveals actress Shabana Azmi. Blanchett will be in Delhi for the annual summit on November 20.*Cate Blanchett*
